attempt_description:
Start with B;
End with A;
Middle content (if any) consists only of A and B, in any quantity (including empty)

A string composed of a and b, where:

- All a's are either standalone or appear in the form of ba;
- All b's are either standalone or appear in the form of ab;
- The string may end with an optional a.

The first half consists of repeated single 'a' or 'ba' (cannot have consecutive 'aa');

An optional 'bb' in the middle (but no other form of consecutive 'b' is allowed);

The second half consists of repeated single 'a' or 'ab' (cannot have consecutive 'bb').
